  "name": "Invincible Smile",
  "type": "feat",
  "_id": "eKrGp90zeUftJZtT",
  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Clans/Oshi.png",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 7th level, you've constructed a detailed facade, never allowing prying eyes to find out anything about you. Creatures cannot tell whether you have been affected by their effects at first glance, be it damage or otherwise. They must make an Insight check vs. your passive Deception as an action to see through this facade. If they would succeed, you can reactivate this feature as an action, twice per rest. At 11th level, you may do so as a bonus action.</p><p>You gain a +1 to your AC, Attack Rolls, Damage Rolls, Saving Throws, and Save DCs against creatures unaware of this facade. This bonus increases to +2 at 15th level and +3 at 18th level.</p>",
      "chat": ""
    },
